data.description: Game room with French doors and formal dining room with hardwood floors. Extended entry leads to large family room with ceramic tile floor, a corner cast stone fireplace and a wall of windows. Kitchen features island with built-in seating space and walk-in pantry. Private master suite with a wall of windows. Master bath includes corner garden tub, separate glass-enclosed shower, dual vanities, large walk-in closet and a linen closet. Secondary bedrooms and a Hollywood bath complete the open design. Extended covered backyard patio. Sprinkler system. Two-car garage.
